{"tid":1930776,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[肺炎居家學習系列] 給白痴仔的Programming教學 3","createTime":"2020-03-17T19:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T14:58:59.000Z","uid":352315,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ae1bfeaa21d94ccb043656655923e10279f45a","tid":1930776,"uid":352315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T19:23:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QjcluWs7pg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6QjcluWs7pg&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBwEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=b2990067\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6QjcluWs7pg</a><br />\n終於黎到第三集了，開始會講啲深課題<br />\n迴圈係programming精華嘅部分<br />\n如果識用可以玩到好多野出黎<br />\n<br />\n最基本嘅迴圈係叫遞歸(Recursion)<br />\n例子可以睇下呢兩張圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b3/Screenshot_Recursion_via_vlc.png/128px-Screenshot_Recursion_via_vlc.png\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0f/Droste_cacao_100gr_blikje%2C_foto_02.JPG/220px-Droste_cacao_100gr_blikje%2C_foto_02.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F0%2F0f%2FDroste_cacao_100gr_blikje%252C_foto_02.JPG%2F220px-Droste_cacao_100gr_blikje%252C_foto_02.JPG&h=d860efbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打program用遞歸嘅目的係為咗將問題拆到好細好細：當問題變到好細果陣，自然容易解決<br />\n<br />\n但係遞歸用得唔好可能會造成嚴重後果，例如呢個句子：<br />\n從前有座山，山上面有個和尚，和尚講緊個故事，個故事係：從前有座山，山上面有個和尚，和尚講緊個故事，個故事係...<br />\n<br />\n上面呢句就係遞歸失敗嘅例子，因為問題從來無變易過，一個不斷重複嘅program好可能會造成死機：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.stack.imgur.com/uUNUz.png\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下大家反應如何，會陸陸續續拍多啲自己鍾意嘅課題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（e.g. PS/AI，微積分，dse物理數學）<br />\n希望大家可以俾多啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟FB專頁<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/8gava\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F8gava&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzBwEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=448ddfc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/8gava</a>"},{"pid":"5baca0af8fb62fbbba2d333b1ef9dcfe341b6707","tid":1930776,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n但點解開係創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cc4de8f13161818cbd12292fedca4ea82aec28","tid":1930776,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T19:52:13.000Z","msg":"巴打用邊本書?"},{"pid":"57c7ec917f9d5295b29e06ed2c883d740db4b362","tid":1930776,"uid":352315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6cc4de8f13161818cbd12292fedca4ea82aec28","tid":1930776,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T19:52:13.000Z","msg":"巴打用邊本書?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T20:29:11.000Z","msg":"讀書有學"},{"pid":"bf024f2fb1c6dd6f10997cbdebb2e8e8bcf8475f","tid":1930776,"uid":352315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5baca0af8fb62fbbba2d333b1ef9dcfe341b6707","tid":1930776,"uid":137265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n但點解開係創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T20:31:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得打program最大價值係啟發創意，用新方法做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39042e16a44ccbad15e6a49126fa6b4b7635f44e","tid":1930776,"uid":302204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T22:32:33.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770ce7dc4f36084dca00a5656f0716c8e88eb844","tid":1930776,"uid":204689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T08:36:54.00